256
00:20:08,570 --> 00:20:12,050
I'll keep you deeply in my memory,

257
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:16,500
and take good care of you.

258
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:22,830
So, you need to live a long, long life,

259
00:20:24,450 --> 00:20:27,740
so I'll have

260
