00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,200
What are you talking about?

281
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:20,200
I actually feel more comfortable

282
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,700
when he's not around with me.

283
00:22:33,430 --> 00:22:34,460
(Five more years later)

284
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:35,470
Dad, there will be a thing come to the door later.
