285
00:22:35,470 --> 00:22:36,810
Dad, there will be a thing come to the door later.

286
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:38,050
Don't call him a "thing."

287
00:22:38,050 --> 00:22:39,450
You're so picky.

288
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:41,330
Go pcik him up later.

289
00:22:41,350 --> 00:22:43,160
Anyway, your kid is all grown up now.

290
00:22:43,380 --> 00:22:44,910
I'll give you a little one to look after,

291
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:47,210
so you won't be messing around outside.

292
00:22:47,610 --> 00:22:48,630
A kid...

293
00:22:49,180 --> 00:22:49,820
will come?

294
00:22:51,370 --> 00:22:53,800
Master, Bushi adopted a child.

295
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:55,070
We were keeping him around,

296
00:22:55,090 --> 00:22:56,620
but now that it's time for school,

297
00:22:56,670 --> 00:22:57,950
we want him to go back.

298
00:22:58,710 --> 00:22:59,970
Because Bushi got a job,

299
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:01,720
we need to go to Japan for a while.

300
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:04,330
-Please take care of him for us.
-Why does he look like them?

301
00:23:07,790 --> 00:23:09,990
Grandpa, open the door.

302
00:23:11,080 --> 00:23:12,210
Wow, he's so cute.

303
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:14,170
I heard it's custom-made.

304
00:23:15,470 --> 00:23:16,470
Do you like it?

305
00:23:18,250 --> 00:23:19,510
But custom-made is quite expensive.

306
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,220
Should we just adopt one?

307
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:25,010
You sound casual. It's not like adopting a puppy.

308
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:27,510
There's still a lot to think about.

309
00:23:28,210 --> 00:23:29,410
It's not casual.

310
00:23:29,870 --> 00:23:32,010
I gave Luo Bushi the adpotion files.

311
00:23:32,690 --> 00:23:34,090
I thought about it for a long time.

312
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:38,010
And I think our financial ability is okay,

313
00:23:38,410 --> 00:23:39,860
so we're able to give the kid a complete home.

314
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:41,570
We've got this.

315
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,150
We don't have the qualification.

316
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:47,010
Why?

317
00:23:48,650 --> 00:23:50,060
We're married indeed.

318
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:51,830
But what's the point of just making money?

319
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:53,480
You might as well just marry your job.

320
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:58,430
If I don't make money, how can I buy things you like?

321
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:27,030
I wonder what he'll think

322
00:24:27,150 --> 00:24:27,990
when he sees Luo Heng.

323
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:33,130
At least he can take care of Master for us.

324
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:39,240
He'll have no trouble taking care of him, way easier than you.

325
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:42,850
He's so fierce.

326
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:44,540
No one will take care of him when he gets old.

327
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:48,420
Luo Heng has gotten his body ready for the 7th stage of his life.

328
00:24:49,210 --> 00:24:51,420
All he needs to do is pretend to live abroad for two months a year,

329
00:24:51,990 --> 00:24:53,320
then switch up his look when he's back.

330
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:54,270
It should work.

331
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:59,270
Why would you want to custom-make child?

332
00:25:08,370 --> 00:25:09,740
I'm genuinely worried about

333
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,100
what you'll do on your own

334
00:25:13,430 --> 00:25:14,540
if I'm not around.

335
00:25:17,020 --> 00:25:18,830
I don't want to be a ghost,

336
00:25:19,210 --> 00:25:21,470
wacthing you being miserable in mid-air.

337
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:26,000
If you can't deal with it and look for someone else,

338
00:25:26,490 --> 00:25:28,040
I won't let you get away with it.

339
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:35,750
I didn't know you were so manipulative.

340
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:46,710
In this lifetime, you're mine.

341
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:48,710
If I'm not around,

342
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:51,710
you can travel around with Luo Heng,

343
00:25:51,940 --> 00:25:53,210
and see the world for me.

344
00:25:55,380 --> 00:25:56,750
If you are broken,

345
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:59,210
have Luo Heng place you next to me.

346
00:26:00,420 --> 00:26:01,480
It's just a formality.

347
00:26:02,210 --> 00:26:03,290
You have no soul.

348
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:06,860
And I don't know how the world will change.

349
00:26:16,570 --> 00:26:19,510
When you're drunk, you're so sentimental.

350
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:25,790
Just sentimental,

351
00:26:27,970 --> 00:26:29,060
not sexy?

352
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:36,880
No matter how old you are,

353
00:26:37,780 --> 00:26:40,390
you'll always be my precious Young Master.

354
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:13,150
My empty squares started filling up

355
00:27:13,410 --> 00:27:15,650
with the colors I want because of you.

356
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:18,650
Your love gives me strength,

357
00:27:19,230 --> 00:27:20,340
and that's why I know

358
00:27:20,690 --> 00:27:22,520
how to face everything with courage.

359
00:27:32,870 --> 00:27:34,540
As long as you're still breathing,

360
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,270
I will be by your side,

361
00:27:37,250 --> 00:27:39,550
watching the summer flowers and autumn leaves with you.

362
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:44,540
I can be your partner,

363
00:27:44,930 --> 00:27:46,000
your little brother,

364
00:27:46,450 --> 00:27:47,810
or even your child.

365
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:50,260
It doesn't matter how others see me.

366
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:53,860
What matters is

367
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:56,190
I can always be by your side.

368
00:27:57,090 --> 00:27:57,770
Then all is well.
